description: Alexander Gustavo"The Great"Ht: 5'9"Wt: 150lbsSeason W/L Record (1-0)Brock Avery"The Big Show"Ht: 5'9"Wt: 185lbsSeason W/L Record (1-1) Back by popular demand, we have Alexander "The Great" Gustavo returning after a stunning victory against Dominic "The Dominator" Pacifico. We give Alexander a bit more of a challenge this time as Brock "The Big Show" Avery steps onto the mat ready to battle balls to the wall. Big Show has been devoting himself to the gym, bulking up his muscles to prepare for this match. It's a battle of speed and agility versus muscle and power, who will win and enjoy the sexual pleasures of being named victor? Let's get it on!
title: Brock "The Big Show" Avery vs Alexander "The Great" Gustavo
